Comment: 0,0:00:01.95,0:00:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Part1
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說是廢墟船 更像是廢墟艦團啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照正規手續派遣調查隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認是否有存活人員 查明廢棄的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 開始募集調查隊員吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.60,0:05:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從護衛艦上徵集10人 普通成員中徵集若干人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.22,0:05:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.55,0:05:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德 你也來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.90,0:05:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定能發現大寶貝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要個搬運工
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉吉特 沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.94,0:06:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 我就批准吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 帥哥要去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.04,0:06:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們跟來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.18,0:06:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也讓我們幫幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會給你們添麻煩的 好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.55,0:06:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 我們就待在這裡吧 好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.89,0:06:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我的意思是留下來照看我們開來的船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 船不見了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護衛艦去進行周邊調查了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.98,0:06:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.87,0:06:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟這艦團出乎意料地大 多些幫手也好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.51,0:06:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是拗不過你們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.26,0:07:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.18,0:07:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有 有人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德你也叫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.15,0:08:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人 有人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.50,0:08:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是叫了 幽靈也會出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.24,0:08:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽 幽靈可以不用叫！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.07,0:08:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈是 敵人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要迎擊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 什麼都別做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.58,0:08:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是倖存者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.56,0:08:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.33,0:08:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 根本什麼都沒有嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.09,0:08:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計錯了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.57,0:09:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們才是 怎麼會攤上跟你組隊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那接下來分頭行動怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.28,0:09:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.95,0:09:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.77,0:09:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就別囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.96,0:09:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.31,0:09:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這樣如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試膽大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.13,0:09:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們從現在開始就是幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.04,0:09:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去嚇嚇雷德和艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.30,0:09:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人 嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.26,0:09:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 門關上了 而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.81,0:09:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 給我等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.06,0:10:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是皮尼歐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開玩笑 開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.39,0:10:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋皮尼歐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.64,0:10:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來 帥哥和艾米不就貼得更緊了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.02,0:10:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.42,0:10:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們給我適可而止啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.26,0:10:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙 認真一點探索啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.07,0:10:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 莉吉特…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.35,0:10:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 發生什麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.30,0:10:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫院？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.80,0:10:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 這艘船上有過什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.62,0:11:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道這個艦團
Comment: 0,0:00:03.69,0:00:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個艦團和加爾剛蒂亞曾經有過交流
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.34,0:11:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是大約7年前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.98,0:11:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 莉吉特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個艦團的船的連接方式很奇特呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為連接方式是由母艦的性質決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.51,0:11:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連接船自帶連接臂 所以用不著人形機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.63,0:11:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是莉吉特 知道得真多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.33,0:11:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:12:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯托莉亞 我們可是加爾剛蒂亞的代表啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.83,0:12:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 難得得到了參觀其他艦團的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.21,0:12:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 就算是參觀學習
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.02,0:12:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒必要讓我們手動連接船舶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.31,0:12:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.18,0:12:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是覺得見到了許多人 很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.62,0:12:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天教導我的利多那先生 聽說是連接協會的會長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比加爾剛蒂亞的協會長年輕不少吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.02,0:12:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他或許確實很優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.34,0:12:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.34,0:12:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉以輕心可是很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.20,0:12:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怒我直言
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為這次實習沒什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.23,0:12:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得你叫莉吉特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.11,0:12:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為未來的艦團長候補
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.47,0:12:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有必要再次學習船舶的連接方法了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.66,0:12:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦白說來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.11,0:13:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.27,0:13:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就拜託你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.91,0:13:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以指導一下那個組怎麼連接嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.73,0:13:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你們聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是你們的新老師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.80,0:13:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好聽她的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.80,0:13:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請 請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.97,0:13:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.13,0:13:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是已經全部學會了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓他們見識一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加爾剛蒂亞流的連接技術吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.48,0:13:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.21,0:13:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你教不了別人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.25,0:13:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就說明你學得還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.86,0:13:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的不對嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於肩負責任的人來說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.69,0:13:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經驗是最寶貴的財富
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.98,0:13:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你們艦團的做法與這裡不同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.69,0:13:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該也仍然有許多值得學習的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.15,0:13:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.68,0:14:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個去著手我之前說明過的項目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉吉特…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.86,0:14:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉吉特！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.39,0:14:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來人啊 快抬擔架
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:14:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都跟你說過很危險了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.93,0:15:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.02,0:15:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利多那先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.20,0:15:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了這麼多血還說沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.05,0:15:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快抬擔架來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯絡救護班
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.39,0:15:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.95,0:15:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉吉特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.40,0:15:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是來看望利多那先生的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 倒也不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 你是在這裡工作的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.11,0:15:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來進來！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.31,0:16:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.10,0:16:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利多那先生 莉吉特來看你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.63,0:16:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.95,0:16:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.32,0:16:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.56,0:16:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.97,0:16:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前真是抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.76,0:16:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那並不是利多那先生的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我的大意 還連累你受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.24,0:16:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用內疚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.77,0:16:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒昧問一句…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.76,0:16:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個難道是照相機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.16,0:17:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你居然知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.09,0:17:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我按舊世界的設計圖重現出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.76,0:17:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小時候曾見過一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.23,0:17:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能完全手工造出來 真是了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.15,0:17:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它還能用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.53,0:17:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐好別動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.07,0:17:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拍了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.37,0:17:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 突然跑來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.09,0:17:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.58,0:17:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不說這個 發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.85,0:17:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…利多那先生問我要不要和他一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.53,0:17:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我從來就沒考慮過要離開加爾剛蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.16,0:17:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確 我是個孤兒 所以去留都沒有顧忌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.69,0:17:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我有朋友 還有莉吉特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.94,0:18:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都是我重要的人 我真不想和你們分開…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對怎樣看待利多那先生的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.97,0:18:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是喜歡他的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你應該和他一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我不想和莉吉特分開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.46,0:18:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是去是留 在加爾剛蒂亞都是自由的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.99,0:18:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這樣才能結識更多的緣分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是難得的新緣分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.79,0:18:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的緣分？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.53,0:18:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯托莉亞 你一定沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉吉特…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.25,0:19:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.20,0:19:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.43,0:19:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是這艘母艦的動力機關
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次見識
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.86,0:20:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這動力機關被光蟲給弄壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.49,0:20:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光蟲？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.08,0:20:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光蟲這東西呢 不僅會擅自繁殖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.03,0:20:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且一旦結晶化就會變得非常堅硬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然都已經侵蝕到外側了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說明引擎內部肯定已經被光蟲堵成硬塊了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個艦團大概是依靠這個龐大的動力機關
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.53,0:20:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連接著許多無法獨自航行的船隻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.61,0:20:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在遺留下來的大概就是這樣的船
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.15,0:20:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼看來 船上的人應該已經坐著能開的船離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.65,0:20:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.01,0:20:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說沒有幽靈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.26,0:20:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.35,0:20:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈也一起逃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.65,0:20:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.45,0:20:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就…就當是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:21:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 調查辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.42,0:21:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和艦團長日記中的內容也一致
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調查結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.02,0:21:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 收工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.51,0:21:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 結果沒寶貝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.69,0:21:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.13,0:21:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.14,0:21:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 貝羅茲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.04,0:21:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找到什麼好東西了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.12,0:21:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保密
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.54,0:21:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我啊 你這小氣鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.30,0:21:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝殼屁股女！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說啥！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的屁股！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.98,0:21:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.67,0:21:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有幽靈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.74,0:21:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害不害怕？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 有幽靈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.73,0:21:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.78,0:21:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝貝爾！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.99,0:21:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.86,0:21:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊可誇張了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.70,0:21:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 你害不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.69,0:21:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾 米…？
